Spokane_Valley.KEYF-FM:
KEYF-FM is a classic hits outlet serving the Spokane, Washington area. It broadcasts at 101.1 MHz with an effective radiated power of 100 kW and is owned by Mapleton Communications, LLC.


== History ==
KEYF-FM signed on the air on May 4, 1986 with a soft AC format before flipping to oldies in 1991 and then changed to its current classic hits format on March 31, 2008.
